{"tid":1771072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新職業 嘴炮師","createTime":"2019-12-05T14:42:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T12:20:31.000Z","uid":224836,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d33258244e3dc420187bb4b3872306ce0eb03605","tid":1771072,"uid":224836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T14:42:40.000Z","msg":"和理非既手足 請謹記我地係社會可以做唔到既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係乜都靠勇武架<br />\n今次開個新職業比你-嘴炮師<br />\n六月以黎 每次都有地方開花沖突都會有保安鋪頭之類封場/報狗賣手足 什麼有啲濕鳩帶哂路入場大圍捕<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好次次得個嬲字呀 手足入去好難受架<br />\n唔該 每次去到果啲出賣手足既場 由其見到啲比人影過哂大頭 推哂出黎全世界都知果班仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見一次屌一次 大大聲屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔洗怕柒 講柒佢仲怕過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要盡情屌 最多人望越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔洗驚報狗被咬 屌佢老母做得衰咪比人屌囉<br />\n要佢地班仆街比人屌到精神病懷疑人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地既敵人唔只港共中共同狗架 出賣手足既人都要處理"},{"pid":"b50fcdaa935bcca4f3a5143087eeedc2be5a3dca","tid":1771072,"uid":2076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T14:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4pN6bO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4pN6bO.gif&h=f824c62d&s={SIZE}\" />  128 維園見  128 維園見  128 維園見  128 維園見 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MKG48AO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMKG48AO.jpg&h=67817e52&s={SIZE}\" />   <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SrwkGRT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSrwkGRT.jpg&h=06f56243&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0728eeebbb37148037b90a3e1b97796a1bfc1f92","tid":1771072,"uid":172823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T14:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535dd9f62f28212cfd1c4dfd90c119a97e214975","tid":1771072,"uid":224836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T14:44:33.000Z","msg":"唔希望啲手足要試過被咬先知果種憤怒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌得多令佢地柒 殺一儆百 之後可能佢地唔敢賣人架"},{"pid":"58b10f3cdea16df3fbf1f932d4f4073e70945ab2","tid":1771072,"uid":321709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T14:45:23.000Z","msg":"對唔住，借個位宣傳一下，特首選委過半有望。<br />\n<br />\n特首選委戰線 &mdash; 七個同行手足，成立工會，重光勞工界！只剩唔夠四個月時間！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1768465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1768465</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5f03711d113131d47d56edc9f4dce6bc598ac08e","tid":1771072,"uid":224836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T14:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />128維園"},{"pid":"94edae06da08346241adb200d3f4dad98b803890","tid":1771072,"uid":224836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T14:51:21.000Z","msg":"128"},{"pid":"d6d7ed9162a09746e94eb410b5ecb81ebc3d8cb1","tid":1771072,"uid":128603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T14:52:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e8956a2c30035de268854c72bb91b3709c36f08","tid":1771072,"uid":147464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T14:56:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4ce5eaa1b04090a89e8fa01af1766d65901525","tid":1771072,"uid":224836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco